  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3621860/extras/15702d1afbe25ed5e914d0f2f3db0811.avif?t=1748188521\" width=640 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>RAIN;CHECK</strong> tells a short (~30 minutes) story set in a small town, in the middle of a rainy night, about a girl just trying to get by in this world. During this special night, something very unexpected happens, and a storm of events brews ever closer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose how Maria deals with the impending threat in this Visual Novel by Studio Meow Meow Meadows.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3621860/extras/a9c607fcd3560cbe92327e44ace7d23d.avif?t=1748188521\" width=640 height=160 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple Endings.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stylized Art.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Static and Animated CGs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Introspective cows.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bonus Game inside the Game, the contents of which, unidentified to this day.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3621860/extras/261ed7671b77c1d936fbab1ecd6e6084.poster.avif?t=1748188521\" width=372 height=458 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3621860/extras/261ed7671b77c1d936fbab1ecd6e6084.webm?t=1748188521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3621860/extras/261ed7671b77c1d936fbab1ecd6e6084.mp4?t=1748188521\" type=\